<p>
	Footballers Ointment is a therapeutic natural muscle rub is designed to provide a quick anti-inflammatory treatment and is ideal for everyday use or as a treatment before and after sport or exercise. Our special beeswax provides a protective layer over the skin allowing the essential oils to penetrate deep into the body. Made with a blend of natural ingredients reputed to rehabilitate sore muscles, reduce muscle pain relieve tired muscles and prevent muscle cramps. Usage- Massage a small amount of ointment directly onto the areas requiring treatment approximately four times per day or rub well into muscles before and after sport or exercise. The ointment will form a very slightly greasy layer on top of the skin while the essential oils penetrate and get to work in the muscles.</p>
